Maintainer: Lenik (谢继雷) <lenik@bodz.net>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), meson, ninja-build
Standards-Version: 4.7.0
Homepage: https://github.com/lenik/source2native
Rules-Requires-Root: no

Package: source2native
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, python3 (>= 3.10), git
Recommends: bash-completion
Description: convert Debian packages from quilt to native source format
 source2native rewrites debian/source/format to 3.0 (native), strips Debian
 revision suffixes from debian/changelog entries, and optionally removes quilt
 metadata or upstream .orig.tar.* files.
 .
 When run inside a git repository, the tool stashes local changes, commits the
 conversion, then restores the stash so unrelated work-in-progress stays intact.
